.Ss BUTTON SETTINGS
In the settings that follow, '*' can be replaced by the 'name' as follows:
.Bl -column "maximize" "State" -offset indent
.It Sy "Name" Ta Sy "Toggle State"
.It Li "close" Ta "-"
.It Li "iconify" Ta "-"
